ygData.messageBody:
Items found in unrest: Bronze armor, bronze weapons, FS weapons (all of the formentioned is mostly found off various skels and such..), ivory braclets (off the hand), dusty blood stained gloves, savants cap (off carrion ghouls), and i could go on and on and on and on, but i think ill stop here :) I hope this helps you some.
Wes Lobdell,

is that no one has bothered to make contact with us.+ACI-
